{"id": "art-167", "label": "Art. 167", "title": "Art. 167: Numirea unui curator special", "slug": "art-167", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_424899909\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1242\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_424899909\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 167: Numirea\nunui curator special </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_848030182\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1241\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_848030182\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>În caz de nevoie &#351;i pân&#259; la solu&#355;ionarea\ncererii de instituire a consilierii judiciare sau a tutelei speciale,\ninstan&#355;a de tutel&#259; poate numi un curator special pentru îngrijirea\n&#351;i reprezentarea celui a c&#259;rui ocrotire a fost cerut&#259;, precum\n&#351;i pentru administrarea bunurilor acestuia.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}